title: Fédérale 2
text: Fédérale 2 is a <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> club championship division in France. It is the fourth division of rugby above <a href="F%C3%A9d%C3%A9rale%203">Fédérale 3</a>. Teams can earn promotion to <a href="F%C3%A9d%C3%A9rale%201">Fédérale 1</a>, and subsequently, the professional leagues such as <a href="Rugby%20Pro%20D2">Rugby Pro D2</a> and the <a href="Top%2014">Top 14</a>.
